    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>故事与氛围</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Sqube: The Beginning</strong> 带你踏上一个神秘而黑暗的世界的引人入胜的旅程。当你开始这段冒险时，对自己的身份和来源一无所知，周围的世界随着每一步的前进变得越来越复杂。随着你的进展，你将揭开关于这个奇怪世界和你自己的秘密。在途中，你的克隆体将成为你最强大的盟友，但你并不总是能清楚地知道可以信任谁。随着你的前进，谜团变得越来越深。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265300/extras/5663482143f9177ed1e413a2670b7bdb.poster.avif?t=1736424855\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265300/extras/5663482143f9177ed1e413a2670b7bdb.webm?t=1736424855\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265300/extras/5663482143f9177ed1e413a2670b7bdb.mp4?t=1736424855\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏玩法</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sqube 将巧妙的解谜与激烈的动作结合在一起。你需要与克隆体一起战略性地合作，克服障碍，解决复杂的谜题并取得进展。你的克隆体将帮助你到达难以触及的区域，并帮助你避开危险的情况。但这不仅仅是关于谜题——在途中，你将遇到敌人，你需要用你的唯一武器击败他们。游戏结合了令人兴奋的动作与令人满意的射击时刻，将策略与反应力融合在一起，创造出独特的体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265300/extras/5dafd8ff6b937704b4909e426b1eddce.poster.avif?t=1736424855\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265300/extras/5dafd8ff6b937704b4909e426b1eddce.webm?t=1736424855\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265300/extras/5dafd8ff6b937704b4909e426b1eddce.mp4?t=1736424855\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>设计</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sqube 采用极简主义且具有沉浸感的设计，将你带入一个充满神秘与发现的世界。游戏的黑暗氛围美学鼓励探索，每一关都提供新的挑战和秘密等待你揭示。你遇到的每一个结构都暗示了故事的深度，吸引你进一步深入这个世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265300/extras/dfb773cefc00230987f6d02cf324f8f8.poster.avif?t=1736424855\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265300/extras/dfb773cefc00230987f6d02cf324f8f8.webm?t=1736424855\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265300/extras/dfb773cefc00230987f6d02cf324f8f8.mp4?t=1736424855\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>控制</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sqube 提供简单但精准的鼠标和键盘控制，让你可以顺畅地操作角色和克隆体。你需要准确的时机和精心的计划来解决谜题并击败敌人。虽然控制容易上手，但它提供了战略深度，确保在整个游戏过程中，智力和反应能力都能得到考验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265300/extras/88e5c26db1d9915a1ba4efdf798a6091.poster.avif?t=1736424855\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265300/extras/88e5c26db1d9915a1ba4efdf798a6091.webm?t=1736424855\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3265300/extras/88e5c26db1d9915a1ba4efdf798a6091.mp4?t=1736424855\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
